kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: add-song-to-playlist-
spec:
  entrypoint: add-song-to-playlist
  templates:
  - name: add-song-to-playlist
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: add-song
        template: add-song-to-playlist
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: user_ID
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.user_ID }}'
          - name: playlist_ID
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.playlist_ID }}'
          - name: song_name
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.song_name }}'
  - name: add-song-to-playlist
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: user_ID
      - name: playlist_ID
      - name: song_name
    container:
      image: python:3.8
      command: [python, -c]
      args: ['''
import requests

user_ID = {{ inputs.parameters.user_ID }}
playlist_ID = {{ inputs.parameters.playlist_ID }}
song_name = "{{ inputs.parameters.song_name }}"

# Assuming the API endpoint is available
url = "http://api.example.com/addSongToPlaylist"

response = requests.post(url, json={"user_ID": user_ID, "playlist_ID": playlist_ID, "song_name": song_name})

print(response.json())
''']

    parameters:
    - name: user_ID
      value: '123'  # Example user ID for Emma
    - name: playlist_ID
      value: '456'  # Example playlist ID for "Classic Disco Hits"
    - name: song_name
      value: 'Hey Jude'
